<plot>Still Chainsaw After All These Years is a documentary by the late Robert A Burns, art director of the original Texas Chainsaw Massacre. It details the goings on of a horror convention called Cinema Wasteland in Cleveland, Ohio and the celebrity guests attending, including cast and crew from the first four Texas Chainsaw Massacre films.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?515772</url></doc>
